---
import Button from '@/components/common/Button.astro';
import { SITE } from '@/utils/constants';
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-36">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-primary-medium dark:text-primary-light tracking-wide mb-4">
        해양·기상 데이터 전문기업
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        해양·기상 데이터를<br />
        <span class="text-primary dark:text-primary-light">연결하는 기술</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        더 정확한 예측과 더 안전한 의사결정을 만듭니다.<br class="hidden md:block" />
        관측장비, 데이터 수집, 수치모델, GIS 시각화, 관제시스템까지 통합 제공합니다.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <Button href={`${SITE.base}/services`} size="lg">서비스 보기</Button>
        <Button href={`${SITE.base}/contact`} variant="outline" size="lg">문의하기</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Background decoration -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -z-10 w-96 h-96 bg-primary-light/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -z-10 w-64 h-64 bg-primary-medium/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
</section>
